Version 0.9:
 - Unlimited quota (0B) implemented
 - Scrambler plugin supported
 - Host selection implemented
 - Remember geometry and state of the window when closed
 - After creating a new mail, the filter was discarded. Kept now.
 - Postgrey-Filter (whitelisting of recipients)
 - Enabling / Disabling spam filtering through Amavis / Spamassassin
 - Enabling / Disabling virus scan through Amavis / ClamAV
 - (Planned and necessary:) Encrypting / Decrypting of all mails
